cast.overview: The feel-good story of Michael 'Eddie' Edwards, an unlikely but courageous British ski-jumper who never stopped believing in himself—even as an entire nation was counting him out. With the help of a rebellious and charismatic coach, Eddie takes on the establishment and wins the hearts of sports fans around the world by making an improbable and historic showing at the 1988 Calgary Winter Olympics.
cast.title: Eddie the Eagle

cast.overview: The story of Elton John's life, from his years as a prodigy at the Royal Academy of Music through his influential and enduring musical partnership with Bernie Taupin.
cast.title: Rocketman

details.biography: Graham Fletcher-Cook was born on November 3, 1963 in Edmonton, London, England, UK. He was an actor and director, known for Rocketman (2019), A Little Romance (1979) and Sid and Nancy (1986). He was married to Jeanette. He died in 2019 in the UK.
details.name: Graham Fletcher-Cook
